name: Treadmill
Description: A treadmill is a device generally used for walking, running, or climbing while staying in the same place.

name: Elliptical trainer
Description: An elliptical trainer or cross-trainer is a stationary exercise machine used to stair climb, walk.

name: Dumbbell
Description: The dumbbell, a type of free weight, is a piece of equipment used in weight  with one in each hand.

name: Rowing machine
Description: An indoor rower, or rowing machine, is a machine used to simulate the action of watercraft rowing .

name: Kettlebell
Description: In weight training, a kettlebell is a cast-iron or cast-steel ball with a handle attached to the top.

name: Smith Machine
Description: The Smith machine is a weight machine used for weight training. It consists of a barbell that is fixed.
